title: CUHK Delivers over 1,000 Mooncakes to the Elderly (The Chinese University of Hong Kong)
text: ( Source : The Chinese University of Hong Kong ) CUHK mooncakes, introduced by The Chinese University of Hong Kong (CUHK) for the first time this year with 'CUHK' printed on them, have received an overwhelming response from CUHK staff, alumni
